{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e0785-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3677"},"text":"§ 3677.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contracts for lease or use of vessels for a term of greater than two years but less than five years: prior notice to congressional committees","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of a military department may make a contract for the lease of a vessel or for the provision of a service through use by a contractor of a vessel, the term of which is for a period of greater than two years, but less than five years, only if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e0786-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the Secretary has notified the congressional defense committees of the proposed contract and included in such notification—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e0787-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a detailed description of the terms of the proposed contract and a justification for entering into the proposed contract rather than obtaining the capability provided for by the lease, charter, or services involved through purchase of the vessel;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e0788-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a determination that entering into the proposed contract as a means of obtaining the vessel is the most cost-effective means of obtaining such vessel; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e0789-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a plan for meeting the requirement provided by the proposed contract upon completion of the term of the lease contract; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e078a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3677/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a period of 60 days has expired following the date on which notice was received by such committees.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e078b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added and amended ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tXVIII/s1825/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title XVIII, § 1825(a)","children":[],"tail":", (i), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/4206"},"text":"134 Stat. 4206","children":[],"tail":", 4208.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaa2e078c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaa2e078d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idaa2e078e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading",